    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "The blade of this *+1 striking dagger* is made from the thigh bone of a canine that died in the act of protecting its master. A werecreature or other creature willingly under the effects of a non-permanent polymorph effect damaged by a *dog-bone knife* must attempt a DC 19 Will save or immediately revert to its natural form\u2014this has no effect on a creature unwillingly polymorphed. On a successful save, the creature is temporarily immune to this effect for 1 minute. Kushtakas and other creatures vulnerable to canines take a \u20132 circumstance penalty to saves against this effect, and this weapon overcomes any resistance such creatures have to physical attacks.",
        "level": 5,
        "traits": [
            {
